<item>
 <title>Not arrested, now photographing in San Miguel de Allende</title>
 <link>http://www.neilmeyerhoff.com/content/not-arrested-now-photographing-san-miguel-de-allende</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;When I last wrote we were outside the police station waiting to find out if the driver or vehicle were going to be in trouble. Just a few minutes later we were on our way. We don&#039;t know how the issue of transporting tourists without a tourist license plate was resolved. We arrived in San Miguel about on time as the drivers way exceed the speed limits to make up time.&lt;/p&gt;
